name: application-PendingAcceptance
subject: Your [[badge_type_name]] registration for [[event.display_name]]
body:
Good evening!

Thank you so much for your patience. We want to congratulate you, your [[badge_type_name]] application for **[[display_name]]** has been approved for **[[event.display_name]]**. We are very excited for this year as we have condensed the hall to a single room. In the smaller room's place, the After Dark Hall shall be set up on Thursday load-in in the evening. 

**Actions required:** 

- Please use the following link to review our Vendor Information Packet, which will contain all you need to know to vend at  [[event.display_name]]. **Please read the document in it's entirety before proceeding:** [Vendor Information Packet](https://docs.google.com/document/d/e/2PACX-1vSW0cYZoYjlS2V8iBQN5pU-bAkHZNXcnXSIzvq5tc2zFuCBoJGPlPhLjNA-zxTw5sd0ikwYVmLr7ToK/pub).
- After doing so, please visit this following link to confirm your registration and, if required, make a payment for your badges.
- Your designated location will be found in the Registration site when available, but at this time please refer to the vendor information packet.


Please proceed to **confirm** your acceptance by [clicking this link]([[cart_url]]) to finish your registration.

We cannot wait to see you all soon!

Thanks,
[[event-name]] Registration
